    question: "What is integration by parts?",
    answer: "Integration by parts: ∫u dv = uv − ∫v du. Use the ILATE rule to choose u: Inverse trigonometric, Logarithmic, Algebraic, Trigonometric, Exponential. Example: ∫x eˣ dx = xeˣ − eˣ + C."
